## Features

- Tokio async runtime for high-performance I/O
- PostgreSQL integration via sqlx with connection pooling
- Axum-based REST API with OpenAPI documentation
- Ontology-driven code generation with ggen

## Getting Started

```bash
# Generate code from ontology
ggen sync

# Build
cargo build

# Test
cargo test
```

## Architecture

This project demonstrates ggen's code generation from RDF ontologies.
The source of truth lives in `ontology/showcase.ttl`.
